Keyboard unfocuses in number entry on Settings page
issue.body: When tapping on the radius EditText, the keyboard immediately unfocuses and turns into a normal keyboard with no focus. Tapping on the EditText again without closing the keyboard allows text entry. If the keyboard is closed before trying to edit the EditText again, the problem repeats.
